<P><HI>Ruth</HI>'s RESOLUTION: A DISCOURSE, Delivered By the late Reverend JONATHAN EDWARDS, Of <HI>Northampton.</HI></P>
<P>HARTFORD: Re-printed by THOMAS GREEN, at the Heart and Crown, oppo&s;ite the Court-Hou&s;e.</P>
