no other Portion but this World? <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ow take up that Re&s;olution, th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> if it be po&s;&s;ible you cleave to them that have fl<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d for Reinge to lay hold of the Hope &s;et before them Count the co&s;t of a thorough, violent&punc; and perpetual Pur&s;uit of Salvation, and for&s;ake all, as Ruth for&s;ook her own Country, and all her plea&s;ant En|joyment in it Don't do as Orpha did; who &s;et out, and then was di&s;couraged, and went back: But hold out with Ruth thro' all Di&s;couragement and Oppo&s;ition. When you con&s;ider others, that have cho&s;en the better Pa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t, let that Re&s;oluti<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> be ever firm with you, <HI>Where thou g<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e&s;t I will go; where thou lodge&s;t I will lodge; thy People &s;hall be my People, and thy God my God.</HI></P>
